{"article_id":"JsPf0NlW9O4nW4IO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Michael Cohen , the president ' s former fixer","depth":9},{"id":1,"text":"who once famously claimed","depth":11},{"id":2,"text":"he was willing to `` take a bullet '' for Donald Trump","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"before later turning against his boss ,","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"was sentenced to three years in prison Wednesday by a federal judge in New York","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"after pleading guilty to numerous crimes","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"while cooperating with prosecutors .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Before sentencing ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Cohen ripped into his former boss in federal court ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"telling the judge","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"he felt","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"it was his duty to cover up the president 's \" dirty deeds . \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Cohen appeared before U.S. District Judge William Pauley III","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"for sentencing","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"after pleading guilty to campaign finance violations , tax evasion and lying to Congress about Trump ' s past business dealings in Russia .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"He was seen entering the Manhattan courthouse Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"accompanied by members of his family .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Cohen does n't have to report to prison until March 6 .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"He also was ordered to pay $ 1.4 million in restitution and a $ 50,000 fine , and forfeit $ 500,000 .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Speak","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"ng in court","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"efore the judge issued the sentence ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"ohen said","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"blind loyalty \" to Trump led him \" to take a path of darkness instead of light . \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"ut Rudy Giuliani , an attorney for Trump , argued in a phone interview with Fox News","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"hat Cohen wasn ' t always 